<subSubSection id="C3336575553B56358A900DED1789FB0A" pageId="0" pageNumber="248" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B9636FE553B56358A900DED16ABFCEC" blockId="0.[1259,2137,679,835]" pageId="0" pageNumber="248">• Small to medium-sized mammals with large head, elongated snout ending in a mobile, disk-like nose, short neck, prominent ears, small eyes, robust jaws with long canines, strong legs, small tail, and bristly coat.</paragraph>
